---
title: Tex-Mex Spiced Pork Steaks with Roast Veggie Toss & Smokey Aioli
description: Bright, colourful and full of flavour - those are the makings of all the best meals, including this one! With Tex-Mex spiced pork, roasted veggies and smokey aioli to tie it all together, every bite of this delicious dinner will have you feeling happily satisfied.
